| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1223 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b0da83d7-a9f2-5bc4-8a60-a78c7d77c35b"
